    "The_size_of_your_army,_similar_to_the_armies_of_the_lords,_depends_on_several_factors:^^Leadership:_each_point_will_increase_the_maximum_size_of_your_army_by_5._Companions_with_Leadership_help_lead_the_party.^^Charisma:_each_point_of_your_charisma_will_increase_the_maximum_size_of_your_army_by_1._It_is_your_ability_to_attract_men_to_your_cause.^^Renown:_every_9_points_will_increase_the_maximum_size_of_your_army_by_1._Fame_attracts_followers.^^Holdings:_every_town_will_add_80_men_and_each_fort_40_to_the_maximum_size_of_your_army._These_spots_represent_men_you_can_raise_through_a_levy.^^Bear_in_mind_that_party_size_at_sea_is_restricted_by_ship_capacity._Extra_troops_can_always_be_left_at_a_settlement_garrison,_player_Refuge_(once_built),_or_any_Camp_Quarters.",
    "你的部队规模，同领主们一样受到以下因素的影响：^^统御：每点增加队伍规模上限5人。招募有统帅能力的伙伴可以帮助你领导部队。^^魅力：每点增加队伍规模上限1人。吸引伙伴跟随你的事业的能力就是魅力。^^声望：每9点增加队伍规模上限1人。声望吸引追随者。^^领地：每座城镇增加队伍规模上限80人，每座城堡增加队伍规模上限40人。领地意味着你有更大的征兵空间。^^记住在海上，你的队伍规模受限于你战船的容量。额外的兵力可以放置在领地作为守备，或者是安排在玩家的避难所（需要建立），或者任意岗哨。"
