    "ip_sea_battle_text",
    "At_some_point_after_starting_to_travel_on_the_sea,_you_will_participate_in_a_naval_battle.^^First_of_all,_you_need_to_know_how_to_control_your_ship._You_can_give_the_command_to_row_forward,_fast_forward,_backwards,_or_stay._The_up_and_down_arrow_keys_switch_between_these_commands._You_can_also_give_the_command_to_go_straight,_starboard,_hard_starboard,_port_or_hard_port._The_left_and_right_arrow_keys_switch_between_these_commands.^^Current_commands_are_represented_by_arrows_around_the_representation_of_your_ship_in_the_upper_right_corner._Press_Enter_to_set_the_sail_and_Backspace_to_get_a_tactical_view_of_the_scene._Try_these_commands_to_get_a_feeling_for_steering_a_ship_and_the_effect_of_the_wind.^^As_soon_as_you_get_close_enough_to_an_enemy_ship,_boarding_will_commence._The_ships_are_lashed_together_and_the_fight_starts.^If_you_are_lucky,_you_may_capture_the_enemy_flagship_after_winning_the_fight.^^In_a_sea_battle_where_you_have_several_ships,_you_can_give_a_'stand_ground'_or_'charge'_command_to_your_ships,_which_are_assigned_to_the_ninth_'division.'_The_first_troops_in_your_army_list_will_be_together_with_you_on_the_flagship._The_other_troops_will_be_in_the_remaining_ships._One_can_change_one's_flagship_in_a_port_or_while_camping_on_the_sea.^^With_a_reasonably_large_fleet,_one_may_attack_towns_from_their_sea_sides._To_do_so,_simply_click_on_the_enemy_port_town_and_you_will_have_option_to_attack_it_once_you_reach_it_without_first_disembarking.",
    "\"在开始享受海上生活的某个时刻，你会参与到海战中来。^^首先，你需要明白如何控制你的战船。你可以通过箭头，给出前进、快速前进、后退和原地待命的命令。指示箭头会依照这些指令做出上下变化。你也可以给出直行、右舵、右满舵、左舵、左满舵的指令，左右箭头会根据指令做出变化。^^当前的指令会通过箭头显示在你船只的右上角。按回车键起航，按BACKSPACE 键获得战术视野。尝试这些指令，来获得操纵船只的感觉，并感受风的影响。^^当你足够靠近敌人的舰船时，将准备开始登陆。战船会撞到一起，并打响战斗。^如果你足够幸运，你会在获胜后俘获敌人的旗舰。^^在海战中，当你拥有不止一艘船，你可以做出\"\"原地待命\"\"或者\"\"冲锋\"\"的指令，这些指令在第九条\"\"队列部署\"\"选项下。你的军队列表中第一支队伍，会跟随你一起登陆你的旗舰。其他的队伍则会登上余下的船只。你可以在港口或者在海上扎营时更改你的旗舰。^^当你有一支相当大的舰队，你可以从海上袭击城镇。想要如此做，只需要到达并点击敌人港口城镇，就会出现攻击选项，而不需要先登陆才能发动攻击。\""
