    "When_you_reach_level_13,_you_can_get_one_of_these_traits_depending_on_your_skill_choices:^^Berserker:_Going_berserk_will_give_you_momentary_improved_speed_and_strength_in_the_heat_of_the_battle._This_brutal_ferocity_will_make_your_vision_turn_red.^^Inspiring:_This_acquired_skill_will_increase_your_leadership_in_battle_as_your_war_cries_strengthen_the_fierceness_of_your_men_in_combat.^^Tough:_This_skill_will_make_your_troops_move_faster_and_increase_their_agility_in_the_battle.^^Strong:_Your_preoccupation_with_the_maintenance_of_your_men's_shields_and_armors_will_make_it_harder_for_the_enemy_to_wound_them.^^Use_key_T_to_activate_these_traits_on_the_battlefield.",
    "当你达到15级的时候，根据你的技能选择可以得到其中一个特性:^^狂战士：进入狂暴模式后你会在战斗中得到速度和力量加成，这种狂暴状态会让你视野变红。^^激励：这个技能会在战斗中增加你的统御，你的战吼会加强你的部队的战斗力。^^坚韧：这个技能会让你的部队移动得更快，在战斗中增加敏捷。^^强壮：你会一直保持部队的盾墙状态，护甲也会更坚硬，从而使得敌人难以对其造成伤害。^^使用T键来在战场中发动特性。"
