    "ip_skills_text",
    "When_creating_or_developing_a_character_in_Viking_Conquest,_one_has_to_pay_attention_to_the_many_skills_and_attributes._Skills_like_persuasion_and_leadership_are_essential_for_trading,_wages,_lord_and_lady_interaction,_and_forced_conversion._Attributes_such_as_intelligence_and_charisma_are_also_essential_in_these_activities,_but_will_also_affect_your_ability_to_marry_or_lead_people.^^There_are_three_important_skills_for_the_sea:_'Sea_King,'_'Navigation'_and_'Looting.'^^One's_Sea_King_level_determines_the_amount_of_ships_one_can_command._Level_one_allows_up_to_two_ships._Seven_ships_are_the_maximum_at_the_Sea_King_level_of_four.^^The_Navigation_skill_allows_one_to_travel_faster_on_the_sea._It_is_the_naval_equivalent_of_the_Pathfinding_skill_on_land_(which,_by_the_way,_will_not_help_on_the_sea).^^A_higher_Looting_skill_results_in_a_higher_chance_of_capturing_enemy_ships.^",
    "当你在维京征服里创造或发展一名角色时，你需要注意角色的技能和属性。技能，比如说服或领导，对于交易、工资以及与领主和贵族小姐的互动非常关键。属性，比如智力和魅力，对于上述活动也很重要，还会影响到你的婚姻和领导能力。^^至于海上，则有三项重要的技能：“提督”、“导航”以及“掠夺”。^^提督技能水平决定了你所能控制的船只数量。在等级一时，你可以控制两艘船。当提高到等级四时，你所能控制的船只达到最大值，即七艘。^^导航技能允许你在海上更快地移动，相当于陆上的追踪技能（提醒一下，追踪技能对于海路没有帮助）。^^更高的掠夺技能等级将提高你俘虏敌人船只的几率。^"
